altTitles.en: In the Heart of Kunoichi Tsubaki

description.en:
The isolationist Akane Clan, composed of an all-girls body mainly consisting of young kunoichi in training, has a code to which they all must adhere:  
  
As men are beings of danger, to exchange with them is forbidden.  
  
Kunoichi Tsubaki, the leader of the Dog Squad, is an excellent trainee with a promising future, but she has started to experience a strange feeling in her heart… whenever the subject of boys is brought up.

description.en:
Otaku Kunoichi ≒ Otaku NEET ≒ Girl with Zero Romantic Experience!

A normal salaryman, Tsukasa, is attacked by a Youma and is gallantly saved by the appearance of the genius kunoichi, Shizuri. However, when she is not working, she becomes an otaku NEET... Today, Tsukasa's househusband skills will continue to spoil Shizuri. A prescription delivered directly to you♪

The Comic Walker version of "NEET de Otaku na Kunoichi to naze ka Dousei hajimemashita". The story is almost 1 to 1 with the doujinshi excluding chapter 1.

altTitles.en: おいでよ! くのいちの里

description.en:
On a school trip to shinobi-themed Ninjatown, a young man named Ichi Kuno accidentally springs a mystical ninja trap which sends him back to the Age of the Ninja. Having no other path, he must pose as a girl and infiltrate an Kurenai Academy, a school of kunoichi students, to retrieve a mystical scroll that can return him to the future. But when everyone around him is already far better at stealth and infiltration than he could ever imagine being, it's not going to be easy.  
  
He'll need to employ his own special bag of tricks, and have a lot of luck, if he's going to last more than 5 minutes surrounded by hot kunoichi girls, every one of whom would happily kill him in a moment if he's discovered.

title.en: Somehow, I Started Living With a NEET Otaku Kunoichi

description.en:
A man is the target of a kunoichi's mission, and a lot of blood was spilled for him to learn this.  
  
However, said kunoichi is taking some "liberties" with the mission… Or are those part of the mission too?  
  
Approved scanlation by [@kotatsu358](https://twitter.com/kotatsu358)

description.en: Kohana gets manipulated into "sexual training" by her childhood friend Tora who tells her that the experience is necessary for her to be assigned to a mission where she gets to play lovers with her master who she loves. Will she be able to resist as Tora's demands gradually increase? The answer is no.
